com.github.codelomer.configprotection.api

Class ConfigChecker

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.codelomer.configprotection.api.ConfigChecker

  • public class ConfigChecker
extends java.lang.Object
    Main API Class for Interacting with Input Parameters from Configuration. This class provides methods for validating and retrieving various types of data from a configuration file.
